{"tid":1641750,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黑警喬裝示威者破壞 - 我地爭一條斷正既影片","createTime":"2019-10-09T12:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T14:53:30.000Z","uid":290407,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6a51c69138d446fd205726f1764828730bed814c","tid":1641750,"uid":290407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"黑警喬裝示威者大肆破壞，已經幾乎係人人都相信既事。<br />\n但我地始終得一D零碎既影片/照片，死黑警一味否認。<br />\n如果可以拍到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: maroon;\">一條影片，由黑警開始破壞一刻，直至佢逃離現場，然後 (好可能) 上狗車，咁警方就100%斷正唔認唔得!!!</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n既然黑警咁鍾意喬裝，有冇手足可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">喬裝普通巿民，係附近拍低整個過程????</span></ins></strong></span> 當然要好講技巧應該要夠膽量，唔可以俾黑警發現啦。<br />\n(當然，如果該名黑衣人離開現場後，唔見佢上狗車，就唔好再拍)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">就係爭一條片! 可以逼警方認衰! 同埋令成立獨立調查委員會更加有說服力! 仲有推上國際!!!</span></ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"44d20174bb8e5ff6a3bd44ce1f881ea545920ee8","tid":1641750,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:33:20.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71672a236fc583c2d1ea82cab9d1730ca55a8d9f","tid":1641750,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"航拍咪可以囉"},{"pid":"a5d3f201ae5e02b4954e8e4151e8384bcc25d675","tid":1641750,"uid":290407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71672a236fc583c2d1ea82cab9d1730ca55a8d9f","tid":1641750,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"航拍咪可以囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:41:09.000Z","msg":"ok喎，雖然只限室外，都可以試下!<br />\n據我所知航拍機一般可以連續飛15-30分鐘?"},{"pid":"9dc943f6d7d35a648fef89dab42d65855cf1dcfa","tid":1641750,"uid":133033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"大把啦 破壞黨鐵又唔計？"},{"pid":"b89f961781